ğŸ§Š Liquid Nitrogen Cooling System (Mini Closed-Loop Concept)
	â€¢	Inner coil housing chamber encased in double-walled vacuum jacket
	â€¢	LNâ‚‚ injected via micro-nozzle sprayers onto copper coils
	â€¢	Phase change removes heat instantly; warmed nitrogen is vented or recondensed
	â€¢	Key Benefit: Enables superconducting-like efficiency at practical temperatures, even without full superconduction

