ğŸ” Safety Considerations
	â€¢	Strong magnets can injure hands â€” use plastic spacers and gloves.
	â€¢	Cryogenic liquid can cause burns â€” use face shield and thermal gloves.
	â€¢	Build in overvoltage cutoff and spark arrestor.
	â€¢	Always vent nitrogen outside â€” it displaces oxygen.

